A new Iron Man series titled "Invincible Iron Man" started in early 2005 with the Warren Ellis written storyline "Extremis", with artist Adi Granov.[13]  The series title changed its title to just Iron Man with issue #13 during the "Civil War" storyline and then later to Iron Man: Director of S.H.I.E.L.D. with issue #15 due to the fallout of the "Civil War" story arc. In issue #33, the book changed its title once again to War Machine: Weapon of S.H.I.E.L.D. which tied into company-wide "Secret Invasion" storyline and resulted in the launch of a War Machine ongoing series.
